	(text_box "The INH signal is connected to +3V3_AON through a PMOS in the ethernet PHY. Normally the PHY asserts INH, keeping it high.\n\nWhen the PHY wants to enter sleep mode it deasserts INH, which gets pulled to GND by the resistor here."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 116.84 99.06 0)
		(size 55.88 15.24)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
